window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Nobody said being a Royal Blood would be easy.</p> <p>After getting the magical council off his back, Eli Grayson is finally ready to track down the mysterious figure known only as ‘Athena’ and get some of his questions answered.</p> <p>Unfortunately for him though, finding her isn’t going to be simple. Shapeshifting lizardkin, devious demons and cunning dark elves all stand in his way.</p> <p>His one lead? The name of a reclusive dragoness - ‘The Scarlett Claw’.</p>"; 
